{"content":"<h2 id=\"默认参数\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#默认参数\"><span>默认参数</span></a></h2>\n<p>通用的写法：</p>\n<div class=\"language-js line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"js\" data-title=\"js\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">function</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> func</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">a</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> b</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> ...</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> c</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> '</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">默认值c</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> d</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> '</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">默认值d</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> ...</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">)</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">    ...</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p>其中，需要注意的是，有默认值的尽量写在后面并且所有形参参数不允许重复申明。具体例子：</p>\n<div class=\"language-js line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"js\" data-title=\"js\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">function</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> test</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">()</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">    return</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 13</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">// 函数可以作为形参的接收</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">function</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> func</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">words</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> name</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> '</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">🍎</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> age</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> test</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">())</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">    console</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">log</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">words</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> name</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> age</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">func</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">请给我一个</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">func</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">请给我一个</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> '</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">🍐</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">func</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">请给我一个</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> ''</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">)</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><blockquote>\n<p>对于没有传入的参数，如果没有默认值，默认是<code v-pre>undefined</code>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"剩余参数\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#剩余参数\"><span>剩余参数</span></a></h2>\n<p>可以使用均摊符号<code v-pre>...</code>来接受最右边的所有参数，所有接受的参数会以数组的形式放入该变量。</p>\n<div class=\"language-js line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"js\" data-title=\"js\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">function</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> func</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">a</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> ...</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">rest</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">)</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">  console</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">log</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">rest</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">func</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">1</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 2</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 3</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 4</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 5</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 6</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 7</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 8</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 9</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 10</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">)</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p>但是注意不能这样写，控制台会报错：</p>\n<div class=\"language-js line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"js\" data-title=\"js\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">function</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> func</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">a</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> ...</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">res